### Suggested order of R scripts for Chapter 8

08_RA.R
   Presenting a basic implementation of the RA and the more sophisticated RA(),
   ARA() plus the underlying rearrange()
08_VaR_DNB_data.R
   Worst/best Value-at-Risk for the sum of six random losses for a portfolio
08_Visual_intuition_RA.R
   Visually explaining the intuition behind the (Adaptive) Rearrangement Algorithm ((A)RA)

